Kim Crawley: Writes for different Infosec related sites. https://twitter.com/kim_crawley

F-Secure blog: https://blog.f-secure.com/

Read resources from trusted organizations like OWASP (www.owasp.org), NIST (https://www.nist.gov/), NCSC UK (https://www.ncsc.gov.uk)

Appendix B: Online training

Pluralsight: www.pluralsight.com. Note: if you have a MSDN subscription you might be eligible for some free months Pluralsight access. Check it here.

Youtube: a lot of good Appsec training material on youtube.

Philippe Deryck’s site: you can find a lot of really good training material there. He often updates with slides from the web application security trainings he gives and videos of his talks.
